0 -16 Td
(- Communication management for notices, campaigns, and events) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- Calendar and timetable visibility) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- Leave request workflow) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- Email alert creation, targeting, delivery, and history tracking) Tj
